                "text": "# LLM sentence annotation prompt — PLACEHOLDER\n\nPrompt design for sentence-level subjective / opinionated framing annotation is\nintentionally **deferred** to a later step (see ai_usage/step_logs.md).\n\nWhen this prompt is finalized, it must:\n- Operate on a single sentence as the primary unit.\n- Take optional minimal context (article title and/or adjacent sentence) only if needed.\n- Omit unnecessary article metadata (no URLs, no outlet names) to avoid leakage and\n  shortcut bias.\n- Request a compact JSON output (label + short rationale + confidence).\n- Refer to the task as \"subjective / opinionated framing\" — not \"bias\", not \"gold\".\n\nDo not implement annotate_llm.py against this file until the prompt is designed.\n",
