mas, model IDs (`PROXY_MODEL_ID`, `LLM_MODEL`, `VLM_MODEL`, `MAX_IMAGE_EDGE_PX`), and the two-phase cleaning split.\n\nNext decision to make: concrete RSS feed URLs per outlet block — I'll log that as Step 3 when we implement `crawl.py`.",
